{"tid":283114,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony A9 偷工減料 ? 連拍快過 5FPS 時, 附近有人開閃光燈就出廢相","createTime":"2017-06-14T01:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T06:34:46.000Z","uid":107023,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"246e1b82fc71768ccd9ca074d03967d0b7727d5f","tid":283114,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:35:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://bbs.fengniao.com/forum/9653891.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.fengniao.com%2Fforum%2F9653891.html&d=ZtF%2B5Weu0h1QVM77lB%2BB2v755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f69f672a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.fengniao.com/forum/9653891.html</a><br />\nA9 解拆圖<br />\n<br />\n快門只係 A7R2 的AFE-3379的模組, 被限只有 5fps 機械快門<br />\n當使用連拍 5fps 以上, 附近有強光, 例如閃光燈, 張相就有一半全白變廢相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/093434_1a5d507331b7a584e07c63be132f2525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F093434_1a5d507331b7a584e07c63be132f2525.jpg&h=ddcfb5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係見到有人用 A9 玩連拍, 就可以係佢附近用閃燈, 廢哂佢 d 相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a94a491034a0be8662787b5b94c3fee8cc2513","tid":283114,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:39:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9b863f974a34bd8f5fb833f9ccdfd24fb472c9a","tid":283114,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手呀？理鳩你用乜撚電子或機械快門乜機附近有人用閃而你冇撚用都有機會係咁<br />\n發現新大陸咁笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係未見過附近有人用閃光燈會攪到自己 d 相一半白哂呀, 係得 A9 會禁樣真係笑撚死我<br />\n成班記者圍住係禁閃, 唔通全部人 d 機都一半白哂出廢片 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffc19394bdb0ae47ff995d649bec9f04d838a81","tid":283114,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:56:16.000Z","msg":"以我既理解含撚貓講得冇錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65012d5861639aae3f892d2760a91d19dc941d9","tid":283114,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:04:56.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都會咁架咩.."},{"pid":"36119e5d106661a6f098dca064df99e8e7300a79","tid":283114,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"開閃燈同步唔夠快都會黑半邊啦<br />\n<br />\n有咩大問題？"},{"pid":"b09ac855936c0078b6d6e85ec74b420d4d046e5c","tid":283114,"uid":111701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新手呀？理鳩你用乜撚電子或機械快門乜機附近有人用閃而你冇撚用都有機會係咁<br />\n發現新大陸咁笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係未見過附近有人用閃光燈會攪到自己 d 相一半白哂呀, 係得 A9 會禁樣真係笑撚死我<br />\n成班記者圍住係禁閃, 唔通全部人 d 機都一半白哂出廢片 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪未影過相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c49f17a34974b314b072cc4b6f8c92e157cb76","tid":283114,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開閃燈同步唔夠快都會黑半邊啦<br />\n<br />\n有咩大問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己支閃 + 自己閃燈唔同步就話黑半邊姐<br />\n而家係 5fps 以上或開電子快門時, 任何快門時間 + 任何閃燈 (自己或其他人閃到你), 都爆白半邊 wor"},{"pid":"505d9c6c06eb72585460af0ae6e577cf59d0ede1","tid":283114,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"含撚貓反應咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195a937dc34bd1e2211464492da46cafe8f2e95b","tid":283114,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開閃燈同步唔夠快都會黑半邊啦<br />\n<br />\n有咩大問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己支閃 + 自己閃燈唔同步就話黑半邊姐<br />\n而家係 5fps 以上或開電子快門時, 任何快門時間 + 任何閃燈 (自己或其他人閃到你), 都爆白半邊 wor</blockquote><br />\n原來如此"},{"pid":"b8c187f057929630c35f08703312eaa4a9e978f4","tid":283114,"uid":44458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"其實只係拍video無用快門，60fps都得<br />\n跟本就係錄野, 機械快門單反外應該淘汰"},{"pid":"1dba8e708402d3a6a639cd02d61c7f279d240ced","tid":283114,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:56:38.000Z","msg":"button layout / menu 咁亂既"},{"pid":"085fe50d666d6c00f12132ba4dd92e0146368891","tid":283114,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:26:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82b87c540a7f5a18498edcce0515bde26e4ef947","tid":283114,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以我既理解含撚貓講得冇錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己以前新手都試過咁重上網問<br />\n俾膠能抹noise友笑柒我部機屎我現在重刻骨銘心<br />\n根本光線唔同步就有機會出現如此問題<br />\n出post條友好似發現新大陸咁真係笑撚死我</blockquote><br />\n有無新相示範下"},{"pid":"71e3a2d6d5b3e0a81d0617046b4de58fb5dbf383","tid":283114,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:31:55.000Z","msg":"樓主衝岀黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34cc69802fa6da971429abd0eb54f31d5ec93cc","tid":283114,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:51:12.000Z","msg":"偷工減料係咁嘅意思咩?<br />\nspec已經寫明"},{"pid":"59d8576c499a88d722015311d87bc0a202d38cce","tid":283114,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/125417_4a277291967849d22305a2637c88cac3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F125417_4a277291967849d22305a2637c88cac3.jpg&h=b513e897&s={SIZE}\" />謎底已經解開<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心你做打手都做下功課先"},{"pid":"44bc9af170055ad0eaf19cf2f199